reviews.review_text: Incredible sound for an AUD. Andrew, congratulations on one of the best AUDs, Dead or otherwise, that I've ever heard.  Definitely makes it into the top twenty in my book, if not the top ten.  Thanks for all the hard work, time and money you spent getting this to us.

We want Phil,  we want Phil Excellent AUD quality.  Before Box of Rain the crowd chants 'we want Phil, we want Phil' and they got it.  It brought tears to my eyes when i first heard it.  The band hardly ever responded to requests and in one interview they said they never listen to requests from the crowd.  So to reciprocate to the crowd in the moment like that was really special.  to me anyway.
